\begin_inset Formula $\kappa(\mathfrak{p})\otimes_{A}B$
\end_inset

, which is precisely how we defined the fiber of 
\begin_inset Formula $B$
\end_inset

 over 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathfrak{p}$
\end_inset

 in the first place.
 
